The Yogi 3-Layer Sandwich of Philosophy

The Yogi 3-Layer Sandwich of Philosophy

Forrest Knutson

Nov 28, 2025
View in app

Good morning dear family!

Keeping with Thanksgiving, let me give you a sandwich... of philosophy! This is a brief scaffolding of Sankhya, Yoga, and Vedanta. How they work and fit together to create a whole map for the yogi. In our meditative program we eat these three layers again and again, until the profound truths are integrated, and the delusion of the world dispelled.

Blessings and blissings to you dear yogis!
